  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI Triyaj feature provides general guidance based on the Belirtiler you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical eAcil durum call your local Acil durum number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for Acil durum response.",
