  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Hizmeti, istenmeyen mesajlar veya spam göndermek amacıyla kullanmayın.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Abonelikler ve Ödemeler",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EKurumsal plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tŞartlar",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or İptal your subscription at any Saat through your platform's account sAyarlar",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will değil apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Verileriniz",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Sağlık data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Gizlilik Policy, which is incorporated into these Şartlar by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Dışa aktar your data at any Saat via the in-app Dışa aktar feature, and you may permanently Sil your account and Tümü associated data via Ayarlar → Sil Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "Yasal Uyarılar",
  "tosSection7Para1": "HİZMET, HERHANGİ BİR GARANTİ OLMAKSIZIN, “OLDUĞU GİBİ” VE “MEVCUT OLDUĞU GİBİ” SAĞLANMAKTADIR; TİCARİ ELVERİŞLİLİK, BELİRLİ BİR AMACA UYGUNLUK VEYA HAK İHLALİ OLMAMASI GİBİ ZIMNİ GARANTİLER DE DAHİL OLMAK ÜZERE, ANCAK BUNLARLA SINIRLI OLMAMAK ÜZERE.",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI Triyaj recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "Sorumluluk Sınırlaması",
  "tosSection8Para1": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN Hayır EVENT SHALL {producer} BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO USE) THE SERVICE, WHETHER BASED ON WARRANTY, CONTRACT, TORT, OR ANY Diğer LEGAL THEORY.",
  "tosSection9Title": "Fesih",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and Sil your account at any Saat via SAyarlar We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these Şartlar or if we reasonably believe we are Zorunlu to do so by law.",
